{"tid":936933,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"蒼井空克服不育，拖老公宣佈懷孕五個月","createTime":"2018-12-11T07:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T13:54:11.000Z","uid":70437,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"6a8ae1308474ae4586411eed4d2ca08c28c0dd71","tid":936933,"uid":70437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFpOk6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFpOk6e.png&h=cff6245e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年35歲嘅日本前AV女優蒼井空今年元旦宣佈閃婚，與其貌不揚嘅DJ NON拉埋天窗，蒼老師在閃婚後多次透露希望可以生小朋友，仲一度發福傳出懷孕消息。今日，蒼井空在台灣舉行記者會，仲同老公DJ NON齊齊現身，宣佈造人成功陀B五個月。蒼老師表示：「我很激動，也很感恩，希望我的寶寶能感受到大家的祝福，一路以來我是個幸福的人，也希望繼續努力堅持做自己，謝謝大家！」<br />\n<br />\n蒼老師婚後曾在網誌上承認有造人計劃，無奈發現自己嘅卵子發育不佳，導致未能順利懷孕，並有接受治療，如今終於克服不孕，明年將榮升媽咪達成心願。<br />\n<br />\n來源毒果<br />\n<br />\nSensei <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你老公好偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b970ca4f93b4d6b3487f6a0b55a180d1cd386117","tid":936933,"uid":126690,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:11:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dde034b6dd95f21541286c77ef0110c5c46f92c5","tid":936933,"uid":50889,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:12:37.000Z","msg":"有幾多人嘅 DNA ？"},{"pid":"a84b825a1fa35cadbb53ae7d27e607206d0bc352","tid":936933,"uid":99766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0228f3389171c9ddeecb66701891d68ac163785","tid":936933,"uid":70437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b970ca4f93b4d6b3487f6a0b55a180d1cd386117","tid":936933,"uid":126690,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:11:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JutjsNB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail